百万符合参选资格的香港人之一。」 「（在卸任后的）过去三年里，我并不是什么都没做。」梁振英告诉路透社，他将「尽一切努力」为香港服务、为国家服务。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-47c7732a04dab78ef79079cf7d95866f_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "272 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/447634801"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iy5Hx0vCvvI8zEAMaCDYxNzUzMTAwIIbjg4IGMAM4gQJAGHIJNDQ3NjM0ODAxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1614939023.6858084", "card_id": "Q_433563472", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 152}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "日本人看中国人的姓名有什么感觉？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-5c750e1c7eacd29a5041a785d2350d35_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "264 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/433563472"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iy5Hx0vCvvI8zEAMaCDU4NjI2NDA0ILDIsf4FMA84nQpAGXIJNDMzNTYzNDcyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1614939023.6861408", "card_id": "Q_447313752", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 140}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待陈铭在《奇葩说》第七季半决赛中被淘汰？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-e3ab76e537d073c87f6be6f9061afaef_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "235 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/447313752"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iy5Hx0vCvvI8zEAMaCDYxNjgxNTkzIP3e+oEGMAw4jAJAGnIJNDQ3MzEzNzUyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1614939023.6865504", "card_id": "Q_447095616", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么 2020 年那么强的 TES 和 JDG 突然就不行了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_ar